title: WinSetupFromUSB 1.4
description:
create bootable usb :

-winXP 
------
run WinSetupFromUSB-1-4.exe

[v] Auto format in with FBinst
[*] NTFS  - new PC ( usb hhd format support )
[*] FAT32 - old PC

extract iso to folder ( winRaR )
"add to usb disk"
[v] win2000/xp/2003 > select folder
[GO]

after reBoot 
choice usb ( F12 or F9 for bootMenu )
choice "first part of windows2000/xp.2003"
